# Hits Prediction Model — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A full machine-learning regression pipeline that predicts the **number of Hits** (page views) for
each player in the Muskets Football dataset, using the cleaned `Muskets_data_cleaned.csv`.

---

## Files Created

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `prediction_model/hits_prediction.py` | Training pipeline (run once to train & save) |
| `prediction_model/predict.py` | Inference script for new/existing players |
| `prediction_model/hits_model.pkl` | Saved best model (XGBoost, 2.1 MB) |
