## Pipeline Design

```
Muskets_data_cleaned.csv
        |
        v
  Drop identifier cols (ID, Name, URLs, Contract text …)
        |
        v
  Target: log1p(Hits)          <- handles extreme right-skew
        |
        v
  Train / Test split  80/20    <- stratified on Hits quantiles
        |
   +----+----+
   |         |
 Numeric   Categorical
 (61 cols)  OHE: Foot, A/W, D/W, Contract Status, Best Position
 Median     Freq-enc: Nationality, Positions
 impute +
 StandardScale
        |
        v
   4 Models trained + 5-Fold CV
   Ridge | Random Forest | XGBoost | LightGBM
        |
        v
   Best model saved -> hits_model.pkl
```

