## Model Performance

| Model | CV RMSE | Test RMSE | Test R² | MAE (raw hits) |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Ridge | 0.6985 | 0.7063 | 0.674 | 16.9 |
| Random Forest | 0.5668 | 0.5692 | 0.788 | 11.6 |
| **XGBoost ★** | **0.5372** | **0.5360** | **0.812** | **11.1** |
| LightGBM | 0.5360 | 0.5366 | 0.812 | 11.2 |

> [!NOTE]
> RMSE and MAE are in log1p(Hits) space unless marked "raw hits".
> R² of **0.812** means the model explains ~81% of variance in player Hits.
> The average prediction error on raw Hits is **±11 hits** per player.

