## How to Run

```powershell
# Re-train (only needed if data changes):
python -X utf8 prediction_model/hits_prediction.py

# Demo — predict first 20 players from cleaned CSV:
python -X utf8 prediction_model/predict.py --demo

# Batch predict from a new CSV:
python -X utf8 prediction_model/predict.py --csv new_players.csv --out results.csv

# Single player (JSON):
python -X utf8 prediction_model/predict.py --player "{\"Age\": 25, \"OVA\": 82}"
```

All commands should be run from:
`The-Muskets-Football-HITS-Prediction/`
